      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the Connecticut fur trader.  Collection includes correspondence 
						  (1817-1863), incoming, with some outgoing, encompasses over 1000 letters 
						  about the regional, national, and international fur trade; financial 
						  records (1777-1861), including account books, bills and receipts, and 
						  ledger sheets; and legal documents (1827-1861).</abstract>
